call of the flesh is a 1931 american pre-code drama film directed by william a. seiter and written by robert creighton williams . the film stars william farnum , claire trevor , mary carlisle , john litel , mary carlisle , john litel , charles bickford , mary carlisle , charles bickford , mary carlisle , charles bickford , and mary astor . the film was released on may 2 , 1931 , by paramount pictures .